Package org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.subjectarea.properties.objects.graph

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.subjectarea.properties.objects.graph.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, OmasObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Category, Glossary, GovernedNode, Project
    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, OmasObject
    A Node is an entity in the subject area omas that has a type NodeType, name, qualified name and description. A node may be in one or more projects.

    Nodes can be connected with Relationship s to form graphs. As they may be visualised, so a node has an associated icon.
